 measured in the precedent month and positively correlated with corticosterone levels measured in the precedent month. Symptomatic females were less likely to enter reproductive bouts compared to asymptomatic females. We propose the hypothesis that the seasonal interplay among environment, host energetics, and HPA activity initiates trade-offs in the fall that drive the increase in SFD prevalence, symptom severity, and decline in condition observed in the population through winter.", "access_right": "restricted", "creators": [{"name": "Lind, Craig", "affiliation": null}, {"name": "Moore, Ignacio T.", "affiliation": null}, {"name": "Ak\u00e7ay, \u00c7a\u011flar", "affiliation": null}, {"name": "Vernasco, Ben J.", "affiliation": null}, {"name": "Lorch, Jeffrey M.", "affiliation": null}, {"name": "Farrell, Terence M.", "affiliation": null}], "keywords": ["Ophidiomyces ophiodiicola", "allostatic load", "conservation physiology", "cort-fitness hypothesis", "glucocorticoid", "hypothalamo-pituitary-adrenal axis", "Biodiversity", "Mammalia", "Chiroptera", "Chordata", "Animalia", "bats", "bat"], "related_identifiers": [{"identifier": "hash://md5/1434413c50a1905ceb90698d02173217", "relation": "hasVersion", "scheme": "url"}, {"identifier": "hash://sha256/aad78b4d48b1be0b787fd1124ba45223f5c4f736a8e9f2ab1796761ae225da0a", "relation": "hasVersion", "scheme": "url"}, {"identifier": "zotero://select/groups/5435545/items/335YSRFD", "relation": "isDerivedFrom", "scheme": "url"}, {"identifier": "https://zotero.org/groups/5435545/items/335YSRFD", "relation": "isDerivedFrom", "scheme": "url"}, {"identifier": "https://linker.bio/cut:hash://md5/f4e53c12be6335a548e8dc91af0af099!/b19790-22426", "relation": "isDerivedFrom", "scheme": "url"}, {"identifier": "hash://md5/330417efcaa2560c9b8ebcd6fae17ce0", "relation": "isPartOf", "scheme": "url"}, {"identifier": "10.5281/zenodo.1410543", "relation": "isCompiledBy", "resource_type": "software", "scheme": "doi"}], "custom": {"dwc:class": ["Mammali